    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, representing the pinnacle of automotive care. The exterior paint is entirely flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like shine with no scratches, dents, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather upholstery that feels brand new and all electronic components functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a full record of its meticulous maintenance history. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in like-new condition, offering a premium driving experience for the most discerning buyer.",
      "price": 49500.0,
